<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;ARI&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Ari is a champion character described as a Bastaya of Nine Tails, known for her ice fox heritage and mystical, nature-based abilities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ari is a character positioned high on a tree branch in the mystical forest of Omikai Alan, using a bow and later casting a powerful blue spell."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ari is a fox‑like champion who experiences a transformative moment in a dense forest, holding a glowing green‑lit flower that symbolizes memory consumption and emotional change."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ari is the main playable champion navigating a mystical forest and later a bustling town marketplace, interacting with various guardians and gathering information about Ymelo stones."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ari is the player’s character who holds a glowing orb and performs a sustained magical ritual involving Ymelo stones."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-384453835cabf302cc1866f083c441b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5369aae6f52fc67ffbf63b3db7c1e061&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0faee823efab3399ac6507a90b21a27c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3dba909d410645c865e1539e1cd713d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e403ab6dfb1007767efd391cca7a115</data>
</node>
