<node id="&quot;YASUO&quot;">
  <data key="d1">["\"Yasuo is a champion in a defensive stance, aligned with Ahri, preparing for an upcoming fight.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Yasuo is a champion who appears in the narrative, questioning the need for a bodyguard and interacting with the protagonist about hiring him.\"", "\"Yasuo is an enemy champion in the bot lane who is targeted by S’molder's Q and R abilities, ultimately dying in a team fight.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Yasuo is an enemy champion present in the bottom lane team fight, opposing Smolder and other allied champions.\""]</data>
