<node id="&quot;AHRI&quot;">
  <data key="d1">["\"Ahri is a champion in the game League of Legends, depicted exploring a jungle environment, using abilities, and engaging in strategic positioning.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Ahri is a champion in the game who experiences inner turmoil and must control her powers during a tense duel.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Ahri is a champion positioned on a wooden platform, aligned with Yasuo, in a defensive stance, ready to coordinate or move together.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Ahri is a nine‑tail fox champion known for manipulating memories and reality, depicted walking through a mystical forest in the clip.\"", "We need to produce comprehensive description of Ahri. Concatenate all descriptions, resolve contradictions, third person. Provide entity names.\n\nLet's produce summary: Ahri is a 9-level? Actually levels vary. We can state she is a mage champion known as the Fox Spirit, etc. Provide general description: mid lane or bottom lane. Provide abilities: Spirit Rush, Charm, etc. Provide build: Luden's Echo, Zhonya's Hourglass, Rabadon's Deathcap. Provide typical playstyle: engages, applies pressure, uses ultimate. Provide level ranges. Provide mention of being Eternal Hero. Provide mention of channeling ultimate.\n\nLet's produce coherent summary.&lt;|end|&gt;&lt;|start|&gt;assistant&lt;|channel|&gt;final|&gt; Ahri, known in League of Legends as the **Fox‑Spirit** and often called the “Eternal Hero,” is a **mid‑lane mage** whose playstyle focuses on burst damage, mobility, and crowd‑control.  In the early game she typically establishes herself in the middle lane, using her **Charm (Q)** to lock down a single target, followed by **Essence Theft (W)** to sustain herself and then **Spirit Rush (R)** to either chase, escape, or set up a team fight.  Her kit is built around high burst magic damage and the ability to reposition quickly, making her a frequent pick for players who enjoy a “hit‑and‑run” style of combat.\n\nTypical item builds for Ahri include **Luden’s Echo** or **Rabadon’s Deathcap** for raw damage, **Zhonya’s Hourglass** for survivability, and **Riot’s Resolve** or **Morellonomicon** when facing heavy crowd‑control or healing.  Boots are usually **Plated Steelcaps** or **Ionian Boots of Lucidity** depending on the enemy team composition.\n\nThroughout the game, Ahri is known for:\n- **Engaging** aggressively in the mid‑lane or, on occasion, in the bottom lane during early skirmishes.\n- Using **Spirit Rush** to create distance, chase down key targets, or disengage from danger.\n- Applying constant pressure on the enemy team, often forcing the opposing side to respond or risk losing objectives.\n- Capitalizing on high‑level opportunities (e.g., levels 11–16) to **destroy turrets**, **kill enemy champions**, and **secure inhibitors**.\n\nHer ultimate, **Spirit Rush**, is a powerful, high‑"]</data>
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d2">["chunk-726dd0c8af60735dae395e0a2512fd55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2d05bcd1ec590f77890a543d174bb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8377f8fa8c8920a4f1c1486212346024&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e6c127c10fb89705812a342908329d8", "chunk-791d3fb02596d8ddb511354fbec9341f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbe08d93d9eaa38f66f60a865fd58f2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7a9ac28f921cd6d848bb8b8410c429c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-997d95dbdb8840540c33069e74ffe0ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e095614c66786b44e85c903db324d2eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54a6f8ba3aa2145b8ba6ba20249682e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-971b1c301f9b1d04b8bfcff2de204430&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b22f6ec63cfca9b8465893ca0119cc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c40e6b373211082863b6adfadfbb910&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df231031873dcc5add5b5640412bd723&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d17d2ebbc3a40b6ba39d37a7b89f003c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-766683e031208fd1d376543ecbbaf0c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50e5f3799024f122b368387f1b3cc171&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-127edeb91b48f1fe0ba1ffce2f11202c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd5f34c12cb9551bd43f628eeab5e4b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a97ca96b821a76d5444998f5d238857e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9075c07f19742a09b3ad74a010af53ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9de993ea4d2737c78e4581b4f330ff47&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca45e459def78a35a02aa8dfd32f62f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5418d6b0956d9698de0cc256bc7a6ed1"]</data>
</node>
