<node id="&quot;TURRET&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">["\"Turret is a defensive structure in the game that can be destroyed by Smolder’s ultimate, affecting lane control.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Turret is a defensive structure in the lane that is under attack and exposed due to Smolder's wave control.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Turret is a defensive structure that Smolder keeps near to maintain lane control and push the minion wave.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Turret is the defensive structure in the Bottom Lane that both champions aim to protect or attack, influencing wave movement and team strategy.\"", "\"The bottom‑lane turret is the central objective, contested by both teams, with minions pushing toward it and the enemy team holding it with defensive spells.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"The turret is a defensive structure in the bottom lane that both teams are contesting, with Ahri applying pressure to keep it under her team's control.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"The turret is the objective being contested by both teams in the bottom‑lane, remaining intact throughout the described skirmishes.\"&lt;SEP&gt;\"Turret is a defensive structure in the game that is targeted during team fights in the bottom lane.\""]</data>
  <data key="d2">["chunk-8b662881b81d9f98abf16595ae3bc91a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56760db9e5f22657231001b182fa8f2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-921a2c333f18b12f26287e340c8ea6a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dde3ef385da20ee7d75730ea561e38fb", "chunk-e7a9ac28f921cd6d848bb8b8410c429c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9de993ea4d2737c78e4581b4f330ff47&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b22f6ec63cfca9b8465893ca0119cc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9075c07f19742a09b3ad74a010af53ca"]</data>
</node>
