<node id="&quot;SMOLDER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">We need to produce a comprehensive summary of the data. Entities: "SMOLDER". The description list has many contradictory statements: some say bottom lane carry champion, some say top lane, some say mid lane. The Q ability described differently: long-range Q splash damage fireball, short-range Q/E to poke towers, etc. There are also statements about ultimate: Dragon Practice, ultimate red laser, ultimate pulls enemies and pushes minions, level-6 ultimate. Also mention of other abilities: Q (Scorch Breath), etc. Also some statements about the game platform, level 10, etc. We need to resolve contradictions and produce a coherent summary.

We should produce a third-person description summarizing all info. The best approach: say that Smolder is a champion in League of Legends. He is primarily played as an ADC (bottom lane carry) but can be played in other lanes. He uses a long-range Q that deals splash damage; he can stack and evolve Q to become stronger. He uses his ultimate (red laser/Dragon Practice) to pull enemies or push minions. He is known for using combos like Q Flash or W Flash. He is a high-damage scaling carry, uses auto-attacks after spells, uses mana, etc. Provide details: at level 10, etc. Provide mention of items like Essence Reaver. Provide mention of his kit: Q, W, E, R. Also mention that he has abundant mana and health. Provide mention of his ability to farm minion waves, control waves, and secure kills. Mention of his ability to use Q on high-health minions. Provide mention of his ability to use Q to poke towers. Provide mention of his ability to use ultimate to pull enemies and push minions. Provide mention of his ability to weave auto-attacks after casting spells. Provide mention of his ability to use Q Flash combos. Provide mention of his presence in a video near a river, engaging enemy near turret using a fiery ability. Provide mention that Smolder is a game platform? Actually one description says "Smolder is a game or platform that players use to rank up and is promoted in the video." That seems like a misinterpretation; we can note that Smolder is a champion not a platform.

We'll produce a comprehensive summary. Let's produce about 3-4 paragraphs. Ensure to mention all relevant info. Let's produce a single coherent summary. Ensure to avoid contradictions. Let's mention that his Q is a long</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3e81b71e9a756dcb53e16da09de60616&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b662881b81d9f98abf16595ae3bc91a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c656bbd0a81bad3a9fdd373336233e94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dde3ef385da20ee7d75730ea561e38fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bb8fa15612c7fb77ceb57839a48669e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f57568b2b676851343d311738188737&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38f6b17996dfa4f0725931853356e5c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eec1a77179830c031a31412197497ccf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5df652d0714d2857af1e3e898b9f2fd6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c2817e67c2a0f4eba0e8992bca8e29b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-921a2c333f18b12f26287e340c8ea6a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af73a4b73a0139c676fd73cb1660025e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56760db9e5f22657231001b182fa8f2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d3fc44abada49d7cd74346e3bacb4252&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8052217c808d9d0d02c75c0672fe10cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-668593e769836f1556568b94ee14f49e</data>
